				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/%C4%90%E1%BB%99-H%C3%A1n-Thu%E1%BB%B7-xu%E1%BA%A5t-Giang-H%C3%A1n-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-trung-ki%E1%BA%BFn-k%C3%BD/poem-Qj5cqkU6XffY0rjCvCJQMg">Độ Hán Thuỷ xuất Giang Hán đồ trung kiến ký - 渡漢水出江漢途中見寄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author-k2nQ5fnr9ZRE2MDraIsNMQ">Nguyễn Tư Giản</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/Gi%E1%BA%A3m-t%E1%BB%B1-m%E1%BB%99c-lan-hoa-%C4%90%C4%83ng-Vu-S%C6%A1n-huy%E1%BB%87n-l%C3%A2u-t%C3%A1c/poem-DVCII6fzmdFlJWdhqEYQ_g">Giảm tự mộc lan hoa - Đăng Vu Sơn huyện lâu tác - 減字木蘭花－登巫山縣樓作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/author-wRpSKwqTcKjFpinJIe2YPg">Hoàng Đình Kiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%A2u-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-38/poem-xbGLTClG7iZhtJ5Ofy1aVA">Hồ Châu ca kỳ 38 - 湖州歌其三十八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/author-HbKyCtS3WFreEebdROalkQ">Uông Nguyên Lượng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-D%E1%BA%ADt/K%C3%BD-%E1%BA%A9n-c%C6%B0-s%C4%A9/poem-I6404G0YJU3y4M3QFT-h-Q">Ký ẩn cư sĩ - 寄隐居士</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-D%E1%BA%ADt/author-UALRhalPJa9kMgIlwvUALQ">Tạ Dật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Th%C3%A0nh-Th%E1%BB%A9c/K%C3%BD-%C3%94n-Phi-Khanh-ti%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BB%89/poem-QQHaJPja_YCBlCgf2e06qA">Ký Ôn Phi Khanh tiên chỉ - 寄溫飛卿箋紙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Th%C3%A0nh-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-7BMIfe9m7oAiwp1R4Cezkg">Đoàn Thành Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Duy-Hi%E1%BB%87u/L%C3%A2m-h%C3%ACnh-th%E1%BB%9Di-t%C3%A1c-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-TUfqI8jWPwgMxKmMkeKRjg">Lâm hình thời tác kỳ 2 - 臨刑時作其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Duy-Hi%E1%BB%87u/author-WzPCPKX1v75mZk2s-05fqQ">Nguyễn Duy Hiệu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%C3%BAc-H%E1%BA%A1p/Long-Th%E1%BB%A7-s%C6%A1n/poem-GRcfAB0skBIX7qvYXSz-hg">Long Thủ sơn - 龍首山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%C3%BAc-H%E1%BA%A1p/author-0QmMIpf3jcGx7a8fLthF1g">Dương Thúc Hạp</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C4%83n-quan-qu%C3%A2n-thu-H%C3%A0-Nam-H%C3%A0-B%E1%BA%AFc/poem-pOtyJe5cXlqhAHruAJbTIw">Văn quan quân thu Hà Nam, Hà Bắc - 聞官軍收河南河北</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Giao/V%C3%A2n/poem-O3fis73q7oaTT0_-3zlFGQ">Vân - 雲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Giao/author-flfrki2xpiX5t9QryTYbug">Viên Giao</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%90i%C3%AAu-Thuy%E1%BB%81n-I/poem-u1Nkvtt_r6aL4m896icNpg">Vịnh Điêu Thuyền (I) - 詠貂蟬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
